===Proper noun===
{{Wikipedia}}
'''Celtchar'''
#(''Irish mythology'') A leading figure in the [[Ulster Cycle]] of [[Irish Mythology]] who is an [[Ulster]] warrior described as tall, grey, and ugly, and who wields a spear called [[Luír Cheltchair]], and who killed [[Blaí Briugu]] after the latter slept with his wife [[Brig Bretach]].

